<plot>Octogenarian Eloisa endures a dreary existence in her pristine flat. She is plagued by dreams and voices. There are phantom callers in the middle of the night. And when she leaves her home she wanders aimlessly - into shops and the local church. Meanwhile an ever-present suitcase remains packed for any sudden journey. What - or who - is she waiting for?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?393189</url></doc>
